data.description: Gorgeous half duplex fully updated and ready for move in. Home features all new flooring, lighting, paint, trim, roof, bedroom windows, and more! Bathroom was just fully rehabbed with top quality finishes from floor to ceiling. All bedroom and bathroom LED lighting have a night light feature when you turn it off and back on again. The large bedrooms have spacious closets with automatic lighting when you open the doors. Newer high efficiency furnace and AC unit. The office is connected to the 2nd bedroom and could be used as a sitting room, 3rd bed, nursery, or playroom. Backyard is fenced with a double gate to back up to the yard. Home is also setup for a portable generator hookup to the panel.
